WEBVTT

00:00.068 --> 00:02.203
<i>Previously, on Witches of East End...</i>

00:02.204 --> 00:05.724
Your necklace, it's red.
This is your last life.

00:05.725 --> 00:08.182
You should probably
move along now.

00:08.183 --> 00:10.937
INGRID: You didn't have to do that.
I can take care of myself.

00:10.955 --> 00:13.491
KILLIAN: You have nothing
to worry about.

00:13.492 --> 00:15.755
I just want to make sure I'm not
getting in the middle of something.

00:15.756 --> 00:20.529
It was just a kiss, and we are never, ever
going to tell anyone because it's over.

00:20.530 --> 00:25.285
DASH: I heard you at the library.
I'm leaving early for London.

00:25.895 --> 00:28.826
I'm not your mother.
You knew me as Athena.

00:28.827 --> 00:31.790
- INGRID: Why am I here?
<i>- Serpens clavem.</i>

00:31.791 --> 00:34.509
It's a golden snake.
The tail looks like a key.

00:34.543 --> 00:38.046
I need you to convince
your aunt to give it back.

00:38.080 --> 00:40.098
INGRID: This will end if you
tell me where the snake is.

00:40.132 --> 00:41.643
WENDY:
It's gone.

00:44.480 --> 00:48.023
INGRID: She said one is your soul mate,
and the other, your destroyer?

00:48.057 --> 00:50.191
Does that mean one of them
is gonna kill you?

00:50.226 --> 00:52.672
It's a metaphor, Ingrid.
Tarot cards are tricky that way.

00:52.673 --> 00:54.424
And you think Killian
is the destroyer?

00:54.425 --> 00:57.644
Obviously. All this trouble
started the night I met him.

00:57.645 --> 01:00.935
He's the reason I lost Dash.
Damn right he's the destroyer.

01:00.953 --> 01:02.437
...what, two minutes, and...

01:02.455 --> 01:04.318
So, what are you gonna do?

01:04.319 --> 01:08.543
What <i>can</i> I do? Dash is in London.
He's not returning any of my calls.

01:08.577 --> 01:11.112
He hates me right now...
And rightfully so.

01:11.130 --> 01:12.247
(speaking angrily)

01:12.281 --> 01:13.984
(stops speaking
abruptly)

01:14.039 --> 01:16.776
- Enjoy.
- Freya, I'm so sorry.

01:16.777 --> 01:19.182
It's okay. I am not gonna
let Killian destroy me...

01:19.183 --> 01:21.556
I'm gonna trade
all this heartbreak for good.

01:21.590 --> 01:24.880
Like for that angry couple back there.
Watch.

01:24.881 --> 01:26.961
- ...something that's been going on...
- Look, I'm sorry.

01:26.979 --> 01:29.137
- Let's not do that again.
- Okay.

01:29.138 --> 01:30.986
What did you just do?

01:31.021 --> 01:33.621
Gave 'em a "Rush of Love,"
with a twist.

01:33.648 --> 01:36.200
Damn, you're good.

01:36.201 --> 01:41.289
My life may be in shambles, but at least
I can make someone else happy.

01:41.294 --> 01:43.879
(long sigh)

01:45.504 --> 01:47.211
PENELOPE:
<i>Flore...</i>

01:47.245 --> 01:50.264
(soft whoosh) <i>Pulchre.</i>

01:50.298 --> 01:51.849
<i>Flore...</i>

01:51.883 --> 01:54.752
(soft whoosh)
<i>Veneficus.</i>

